title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 14 - another new build available
description:
In this video we will look at what has been added and what has been fixed in the third beta release for Sim Update 14 which will be released in a few weeks. The fix list contains several fixes related both to fixing stability issues but also several aircrafts including the 787/747 and DC-3 receive fixes.
